g.text: Tools are a collection of scripts to perform different functions
which aren't native to ThoughtSpot or advanced functionality for
clients who have a well-adopted platform.
Scalably manage your table- and column-level security right in the browser.
Allows you to use the vsc/git API endpoints in a developer friendly way.
Explore your ThoughtSpot metadata, in ThoughtSpot!
Manage stale answers and liveboards within your platform.
Enable querying the ThoughtSpot TQL CLI from a remote machine.
Gather data on your existing Falcon tables for sharding.
Bulk delete metadata objects from your ThoughtSpot platform.
Enable loading files to ThoughtSpot from a remote machine.
Tool for migrating TML between instance.
Extract data from a worksheet, view, or table in ThoughtSpot.
Manage Users and Groups in bulk.
